<div class='talk-article__body talk-transcript__body'>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:16
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5634' id='t-5634'>Do I look real to you?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='8133' id='t-8133'>Hope so.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='9797' id='t-9797'>I have no idea if you're seeing this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='11624' id='t-11624'>but I'm just going to look ahead
and trust that you're there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='15802' id='t-15802'>I've drawn a semicircle
in the sand in front of me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='18590' id='t-18590'>so I don't walk past it
